item.title: Aspose.3D for Node.js via Java 23.12 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes information for Aspose.3D for Node.js via Java 23.12. Improvement THREEDNET-1360 Allow export PBR material definition and normal mapping in OBJ exporter Improvement THREEDNET-1416 Use new algorithm to triangulate super complex polygons in .net product Improvement This is the first release of Aspose.
